items.headline: Welcome to the Custom Barney Wiki!
items.desc: Welcome to the Custom Barney Wiki. This wiki is for Barney fans who create their own custom episodes and videos of Barney & Friends and Barney & the Backyard Gang. A few of these were formerly on Barney Wiki. Add your own Barney original creations! This wiki is fan made has nothing to do with Hit Entertainment, Barney's owner. If you want to share your passion with the rest of the world, sign up today. This site can be edited by anyone!
